{% extends 'base-front.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Accueil{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        {#CARROUSEL#}
        <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <div class="myCarousel">
                        <img src="{{ asset('build/images/chatEspace.jpeg') }}" class="d-block w-100" alt="Image de chat dans l'espace">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Envoyez votre animal dans l'espace !</h5>
                        <p>Nous vous proposons notre nouveau service UNIQUE AU MONDE !</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div>
                        <img src="{{ asset('build/images/chat.jpeg') }}" class="d-block w-100 myCarousel" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Second slide label</h5>
                        <p>Some representative placeholder content for the second slide.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div>
                        <img src="{{ asset('build/images/produit1.jpg') }}" class="d-block w-100 myCarousel" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Third slide label</h5>
                        <p>Some representative placeholder content for the third slide.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
        {#END CAROUSEL#}

        <h1 class="mt-3">Meilleurs ventes</h1>

        {% for product in bestSellsProducts %}
            <div class="col-lg-3">
                {% include ('common/_cardProduct.html.twig') %}
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <h1 class="mt-3">Nouveautés</h1>

        {% for product in newProducts %}
            <div class="col-lg-3">
                {% include ('common/_cardProduct.html.twig') %}
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <div class="my-5">
            <h1 class="mb-3">La Nîmes'alerie, qui sommes nous ?</h1>
            <p>Lörem ipsum viling dirack till rett. Nyst sessa radionetik. Mäd fas kilogi blippbetalning. Tujivis rekesade. Kaliga homode. Krososm besm i biktigt om antir. Krosa del. Fadade lesk, samt stenoligen.
                Symisa sosk och kasade. Kar kist. Prerar syktig förpappring. Beföst arad ifall tjock-tv, hackathon. Prepod heterosäligt diktig, klustersmitta. Antenybel biosm. Dolysyren våssa. Pregt våna. Du kan vara drabbad.
                Luktigt gurlesk nuk. Lesperen ade krosertad. Bebest hotelljournalist, fast kektig. Tvodd astrosocial, san. Lun deligt. Mingar dorad, ade raktig. Deng regnbågskväll prelel förpackningsfri. Dektigt onade e-krona.
                Podesk. Tvåmetersregeln ac-förkylning, sodebelt. Pask kaspedat, orade, sunäv. Seliga nedebel afasamma nyreledes. Pren spesk så jivis och plasyfade. Diktig bed. Vintage denisade. Monorade transpatologi viliga.
                Cancelkultur planebel. Dabba ovis rihill doktig. Jarat nyna. Talepunkt pott. Jir degest och anyska vinar. Intrask safan. Ogisk krode kovåktiga. Oskap odagede emedan sofarade i episofi.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-evenly my-5">
            <div>
                <img src="{{ asset('build/images/paiement.png') }}">
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex flex-column align-content-center justify-content-center">
                <div>
                    <img src="{{ asset('build/images/24h.png') }}">
                </div>
                <span class="pt-4 ps-4 fw-bold">Livraison en 24h</span>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                <img src="{{ asset('build/images/euros 1.png') }}">
                <span class="fw-bold">Remboursement sous 30 jours</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
